snippet.title: Episode #96 : Couch Is A Paid Actor — Amber Heard And Johnny Depp
snippet.description:
Both of them were famous actors without a stained past until they met each other in 2011. Since then , their toxic relationship turned their lives upside down, while domestic violence allegations led to serious consequences for one of them.

The questions we need to answer are - who is the domestic abusor in this relationship, is there a basis for calling these allegations fake and if so ,what are they to gain from it?

This is the story of Amber Heard and Johnny Depp. 

0:00 What to expect when not expecting
7:50 Their background
35:20 They meet
39:50 The allegations
1:51:17 Where does the case stand now?
2:01:12 Take outs and outtakes
